title: Don't Call It A Comeback

description:
SNL’s Kenan Thompson, comedian Andrew Schulz, political strategist Lis Smith, and writer Coleman Hughes stop by to debate why it’s been a Hell of A Week on the season premiere of Comedy Central's Hell of a Week with Charlamange Tha God.
